Hier,  chez ma cops, j'ai récupéré ma boîte de Par Odin que je lui avais prêtée il y a un bout de temps. J'ai offert une boîte à son ado de fils, qui a vraiment apprécié le jeu, lui joue désormais très peu à autre chose qu'aux jeux de son smartphone, donc on n'aura plus à se partager ma boîte. 😁
Par Odin est un excellent jeu solo.  Il peut s'emporter et se jouer partout. Il faut aimer les casse-têtes et... les maths. 😁 Pour les enfants dès 10 ans,  c'est d'ailleurs un excellent exercice. Les 50 challenges sont mis en scène par une narration, ce qui est un plus bien agréable. Acheté à sa sortie, c'est toujours un coup de coeur. 
Bon à savoir : sur le site de l'éditeur, vous pouvez jouer à la démo du jeu ce qui vous permettra de savoir s'il est fait pour vous. ⚒ La légende raconte qu’un jour un humain viendra dans le royaume d’Ásgard et jouera aux côtés des dieux… Serez-vous ce héros ?

caption.text:
Взял корпус за 1000р., самую дешёвую материнку под AM4 и видеокарту от Palit. Думал сборка будет выглядеть как что-то из начала двухтысячных, но нет! Смотрится на удивление прилично. Понятное дело что корпус по весу напоминает обёртку шоколадки и СВО туда не уместить чисто физически, а блок питания крепится сверху. Но при этом туда встают даже длинные видеокарты, и сделан он достаточно аккуратно - без острых углов и торчащих заклепок. Видяха тоже вполне ничего, без RGB и массивного радиатора, но температуры и шум в норме. В общем железо действительно эволюционировало в плане дизайна. Пусть по-немногу и не совсем заметными шагами, но всё же бюджетная сборка из 2к19 визуально приятнее 2010го. Только курс доллара не торт...

#FIFA20 Review ⚽️🎮
Il nuovo capitolo calcistico targato @easportsfifa.it è finalmente disponibile! Sarà riuscito a confermarsi anche quest’anno come titolo di punta del calcio visto la sempre più agguerrita concorrenza?
Ecco cosa ne pensiamo nella nostra #recensione:
Ci piace 👍🏼
- La nuova modalità Volta sostituisce la campagna Il Viaggio vista nelle passate edizioni, con una nuova storia che vi vedrà partire proprio dai campetti di strada.
- Volta rappresenta il fulcro del nuovo Fifa e la modalità più divertente del gioco, andando a richiamare l’indimenticabile Fifa Street. Potrete formare la vostra squadra e intraprendere il Tour mondiale contro le altre formazioni sia offline che online.
- La modalità carriera ora offre la possibilità delle conferenze stampa pre e post partita che possono influenzare l’umore della squadra. 
Non ci piace 👎🏼
- Qualche bug di troppo nella modalità carriera ereditato dal capitolo precedente.
- L’intelligenza artificiale presenta ancora diverse problematiche soprattutto nel gestire la fase difensiva.
- Graficamente e nella gran parte del gameplay il gioco è quello dello scorso anno, con pochi miglioramenti. Ad eccezione della modalità Volta.
Voto: 8,5

preview_comments.text: Have you guys looked into adding pressure flips, Impossibles, foot plants , no complies (including no comply shuvs or flips) and slashes (sliding into a back tail for exp on transition instead of having to Ollie)? There’s a lot of stuff most skate games don’t include for various reasons. I’m assuming because of naturally limited space for Inputs/button combos.  I’m just wondering if you guys have thought about tackling some of these common irl but rare in skate game tricks. Is it tricky deciding what should be n and what shouldn’t ? If the game comes out for ps4 after exclusive periods end , I think the touch pad could create tons of possibilities since it has click, swipe and tap functions. I don’t know how those new inputs could translate to other platforms that don’t have a touch pad tho. Anyway just a thought. I can’t freaking wait til this is on Xbox. I’ve been playing on my laptop, which can only take me so far but I’m impatient .

Paperback è gioco di carte edito da @msedizioni che unisce i classici giochi di parole in stile Paroliere alla meccanica del deck building. Il vostro mazzo è infatti composto da una serie di lettere che dovete utilizzare per formare una parola. Più lettere usate per formare la parola più sarete in grado di ottenere nuove carte che vi permetteranno di comporre nuove parole. Inoltre alcune carte, oltre alla lettera, hanno vari poteri come ad esempio permettere di pescare più carte per formare parole più lunghe o  addirittura dare dei malus all’avversario.⠀

preview_comments.text: First in-game day of Hoard of the Dragon Queen(my first time playing it ever) my tiefling swashbuckler got outright killed in the second round of the duel with the champion. Lightning breath hit me for maybe 3/4ths of my health, I returned the exact same number of damage in one hit thanks to sneak attack but I doubt it was even 1/4th the champions hp. Then the DM didn’t pull any punches and hit me with a crit, which is fair cause I knew full well I was screwed(my character had an outspoken death wish as a character flaw and a hero complex rivaled by Batman). Then a coup de grace for good measure. Safe to say I was dead with no death saves. He had the town’s clerics resurrect me as thanks for saving the lives of every villager you possibly could in the course of the first section of the adventure. I don’t think it could have gone better tbh. Fate, the Tiefling Swashbuckler, literally only regrets not dying a hero.
@blueeyesandsafteypins well sounds like he died a hero and now also gets to live as one 😁

Fel (English Fel) - the extreme step of secret magic in Azeroth, demonic magic.  This energy is secret magic in its most pernicious form, because it uses the blood of demons and soul stones of other creatures.  Demonic spells are very difficult to resist.  Warlocks using demonic energy run the risk of falling into the power of the forces to which they call.  Mages who have resorted to resort to fel magic associate its use with euphoria.  If secret magic is addiction, then fel magic is a drug in its purest form, and much more dangerous: it is quickly addictive.  More often than not, a single time is enough to form a strong dependence, as was the case with the orcs.  Corruption of the personality of a sorcerer resorting to demonic magic occurs extremely quickly;  even if he does not become a slave to demons, his character often turns to evil and chaos.  The disgusting yellow-green flame is an external manifestation of fel magic, energy that has become material.  This flame is called entropic fire, it contains infernals, it consists of the "mane" of Mannoroth the Destroyer and some other lords of the underworld.  Entropic fire looks like an ordinary fire, but in fact it is much worse: it feeds on the energy of life, including the energy of life of its carrier
